                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="68253" author="adilger" created="Thu, 3 Oct 2013 16:18:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The timeout is related to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4019&quot; title=&quot;today&amp;#39;s master stick on shutdown on test == sanity test 132: on lu_object_find_at&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4019&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4019&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, the actual test failure is the same as &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3455&quot; title=&quot;Test failure replay-single, test_20b: after 23936 &amp;gt; before 9600&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3455&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3455&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="68251" author="green" created="Thu, 3 Oct 2013 16:15:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;So the reason it timed out is due to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4019&quot; title=&quot;today&amp;#39;s master stick on shutdown on test == sanity test 132: on lu_object_find_at&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4019&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4019&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (already fixed).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="68159" author="utopiabound" created="Wed, 2 Oct 2013 16:05:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This may be affected by the patch on &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3626&quot; title=&quot;replay-single test_20b: @@@@@@ FAIL: test_20b failed with 3&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3626&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3626&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, namely &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7676&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7676&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="68158" author="utopiabound" created="Wed, 2 Oct 2013 16:04:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This seems to fail like &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3455&quot; title=&quot;Test failure replay-single, test_20b: after 23936 &amp;gt; before 9600&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3455&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3455&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; with a large after and a small before, but it times out instead of just erroring out.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
